Position PurposeTo manage and responsible on comfortable office environment and working space/facility in head office for Bayer Group in Indonesia Major Responsibility Areas Responsible on head office space measurement, office movement and renovation (as contact person to building management in relation with office renovation)Responsible on head office maintenance, electricity, electronic related matters, communication (Telkom related)Responsible on company furniture repair and modification, auction on office equipment/furniture, cabling arrangement and cabling tidinessResponsible on payment related to office space to building management (office space rental & services, storage, parking space), overtime on electricity & air condition, and phoneExpenses Responsible & coordinate on OM driver & pool cars requirement (gasoline, toll, parking fee, etc.)Responsible on company maintenance contract & services for facsimile, photocopy machine & typewriterResponsible on driver assignment based on pool car requests in e-Car BookingResponsible on OM administration requirement (filling, payments and OM matters)Responsible on company securityMake sure no compliance in job holder working area Position Requirements Good coordination, interpersonal and communication skill2 - 3 years experiences in Office ManagementIdentify problem for solutionsConsistent, good attention to environmentHonest, responsible and cooperative to all colleaguesGood English written and spoken, and computer skills Kindly apply by submitting your CV before the closing date shown above to:Before May 8, 2014PT. Bayer IndonesiaBayer Group PlatformJl. Jend. Sudirman Kav. 10 – 11Jakarta 10220Email: yasmidar.angreni@bayer.com
